          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Thomas Jefferson Public Service Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill sets the annual rate of pay to $1 for a Member of Congress who has served six consecutive full terms as a Member of the House of Representatives or two consecutive full terms as a Senator and also prohibits such service from being included as creditable service for federal retirement purposes.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-17T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
